d 'ADOINSTALL': module to install Stata packages in a specified path
d
d     adoinstall is a wrapper around ssc install and net install to
d allow installation of Stata packages in a specified path.  The
d command should be used to install user-written commands to a path
d other than the default PLUS directory. 
